{"openapi":"3.1.0","info":{"title":"Solar + EV Integration Sizing API","description":"\n## The only API that correctly co-sizes solar and EV charging\nMost solar calculators ignore EV load entirely.\nMost EV charging calculators ignore solar production.\nThis API models the combined system correctly.\n### What a single API call returns\n| Data | Source |\n|---|---|\n| EV annual electricity consumption | EPA fueleconomy.gov (2024) — 16 vehicles |\n| Combined solar system size | PVWatts V8 (NREL/TP-6A20-62641) |\n| Extra panels needed for EV | Home + EV co-sizing calculation |\n| TOU charging cost comparison | State PUC rate filings (2024) |\n| Solar charging cost savings | NREL Solar+EV study (2023) |\n| V2H backup power assessment | Ford/Nissan/Rivian V2H specifications |\n| Battery storage recommendation | NEM policy + EV load analysis |\n| Full 25-year financial model | Combined home + EV + solar cashflow |\n### Pricing\n- **Free:** $0/mo — 5 calls/min — quick sizing estimate\n- **Pro:** $49/mo — 1,000 calls/hr — full analysis + 25yr cashflow + battery sizing\n- **Bundle:** $149/mo — All 5 Solar APIs\n","contact":{"name":"Tinashe Bethel","url":"https://rapidapi.com/bethelnedi"},"version":"1.0.0"},"paths":{"/":{"get":{"tags":["Info"],"summary":"Root","operationId":"root__get","responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{}}}}}}},"/health":{"get":{"tags":["Info"],"summary":"Health","operationId":"health_health_get","responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{}}}}}}},"/pricing":{"get":{"tags":["Info"],"summary":"Pricing","operationId":"pricing_pricing_get","responses":{"200":{"description":"Successful Response","content":{"application/json":{"schema":{}}}}}}},"/size/quick":{"post":{"tags":["Sizing"],"summary":"Quick Size","description":"**Quick co-sizing estimate. Free plan.**\nSend ZIP code, monthly bill (without EV), EV model, and annual miles.\nGet back: EV annu